data.description: Charming 3 bed, 2 bath home with no HOA in Las Vegas. This versatile property features an office/den that can double as a 4th bedroom. Modern kitchen boasts new counters and all appliances - stove/oven, dishwasher, washer, and dryer - are just 2 years old. The HVAC system is 5 years young, and the roof was redone 7 years ago. Brand new carpets invite comfort in the bedrooms. Enjoy the convenience of a covered patio and an insulated storage unit in the backyard. Centrally located, you're minutes from Spring Valley Medical Hospital, Allegiant Football Stadium, the 215 beltway, Las Vegas Strip, and the airport. Your ideal Vegas lifestyle awaits!
